The evidence with the title 'Wind power in Texas - Wikipedia ' says Wind power in Texas consists of many wind farms with a total installed nameplate capacity of 22,637 mw from over 40 different projects . Texas produces the most wind power of any U.S. state . According to ERCOT (Energy Reliability Council Of Texas ) , wind power accounted for at least 15.7 % of the electricity generated in Texas ... While there are over 10,700 wind turbines currently operating in Texas to  ... 
